<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Genre Manager Mockup</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: 'class',
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        slate: {
                            850: '#1e293b',
                            900: '#0f172a',
                            950: '#020617',
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        /* Custom Scrollbar */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #1e293b; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #475569; border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #64748b; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618005182384-a83a8bd57fbe?q=80&w=2564&auto=format&fit=crop')] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat bg-blend-multiply">

    <!-- Modal Overlay -->
    <div class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/70 backdrop-blur-md flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-50">
        
        <!-- Modal Content -->
        <div class="bg-slate-900 w-full max-w-4xl h-[80vh] rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-slate-700 flex flex-col overflow-hidden animate-fade-in-up">
            
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="px-6 py-4 border-b border-slate-700 flex justify-between items-center bg-slate-800/50">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="p-2 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">장르 스타일 관리자</h2>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">스토리 생성에 사용할 장르와 프롬프트를 관리합니다.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="p-2 hover:bg-slate-700 rounded-full transition-colors text-slate-400 hover:text-white">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Body (Split View) -->
            <div class="flex-1 flex overflow-hidden">
                
                <!-- Left Sidebar: List -->
                <div class="w-1/3 border-r border-slate-700 bg-slate-900/50 flex flex-col">
                    <div class="p-4 border-b border-slate-700">
                        <button class="w-full py-3 px-4 bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 text-white rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-lg shadow-purple-900/20">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
                            </svg>
                            새 장르 추가
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-3 space-y-2">
                        <!-- Item: Active -->
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-800 border border-purple-500/50 rounded-xl cursor-pointer shadow-md transition-all relative group">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                                <span class="font-bold text-purple-300">불륜/외도 의심</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-300">기본</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 line-clamp-1">배우자의 이상한 행동, 의심과 반전</p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Item -->
                        <div class="p-3 hover:bg-slate-800 border border-transparent hover:border-slate-700 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-all group">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                                <span class="font-bold text-slate-300 group-hover:text-white">친구/동창 관계</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-300">기본</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 group-hover:text-slate-400 line-clamp-1">옛 친구 재회, 동창회 이야기</p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Item: Custom -->
                        <div class="p-3 hover:bg-slate-800 border border-transparent hover:border-slate-700 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-all group">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                                <span class="font-bold text-blue-400 group-hover:text-blue-300">오피스 스릴러</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-400 rounded border border-blue-800/50">커스텀</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 group-hover:text-slate-400 line-clamp-1">회사 내 암투와 비밀스러운 관계</p>
                        </div>
                         <!-- Item: Custom -->
                         <div class="p-3 hover:bg-slate-800 border border-transparent hover:border-slate-700 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-all group">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                                <span class="font-bold text-blue-400 group-hover:text-blue-300">납량특집 공포</span>
                                <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-400 rounded border border-blue-800/50">커스텀</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 group-hover:text-slate-400 line-clamp-1">여름밤의 무서운 이야기</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right Content: Editor -->
                <div class="w-2/3 bg-slate-900 p-6 flex flex-col overflow-y-auto">
                    
                    <!-- Editor Header -->
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-6">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">장르 상세 편집</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">선택된 장르의 설정을 수정합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <button class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-red-400 hover:bg-red-950/30 border border-red-900/50 rounded-lg transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3.5 w-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16" />
                                </svg>
                                삭제
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Form -->
                    <div class="space-y-5 flex-1">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <div class="space-y-1.5">
                                <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">장르 이름</label>
                                <input type="text" value="불륜/외도 의심" class="w-full bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all" placeholder="장르 이름을 입력하세요">
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-1.5">
                                <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">장르 ID</label>
                                <input type="text" value="affair-suspicion" disabled class="w-full bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-slate-500 cursor-not-allowed">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-1.5">
                            <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">설명 (UI 표시용)</label>
                            <input type="text" value="배우자의 이상한 행동, 의심과 반전" class="w-full bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all" placeholder="간단한 설명을 입력하세요">
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-1.5 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                                <label class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">시스템 프롬프트 설정</label>
                                <span class="text-[10px] text-purple-400 bg-purple-900/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-purple-500/20">AI 지침</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative flex-1 min-h-[300px]">
                                <textarea class="w-full h-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm text-slate-300 font-mono leading-relaxed focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent outline-none resize-none custom-scrollbar">
[장르: 불륜/외도 의심]

🔥 **필수 규칙: 사용자 입력을 반드시 따르세요.**
- **키워드**: "{{TOPIC}}"을 대본의 핵심 소재로 사용
- **타겟 연령**: {{TARGET_LABEL}} 연령대에 맞는 어투

**핵심 콘셉트:**
배우자(또는 연인)의 수상한 행동을 발견하고 외도를 의심하다가...

**스토리 구조:**
1. **훅 (1문장)**: 의심 상황으로 시작
2. **의심의 증거들 (3-4문장)**: 구체적 행동 나열
3. **추적/확인 (3-4문장)**: 긴장감 고조
4. **반전 + CTA**: 의외의 진실 또는 복수
                                </textarea>
                                <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 flex gap-2">
                                    <button class="p-1.5 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-400 hover:text-white rounded-lg border border-slate-700 transition-colors" title="전체 화면">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 8V4m0 0h4M4 4l5 5m11-1V4m0 0h-4m4 0l-5 5M4 16v4m0 0h4m-4 0l5-5m11 5l-5-5m5 5v-4m0 4h-4" />
                                        </svg>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">* {{TOPIC}}, {{TARGET_LABEL}} 등의 변수를 사용하여 동적으로 내용을 구성할 수 있습니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Footer Actions -->
                    <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-slate-800 flex justify-end gap-3">
                        <button class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">
                            취소
                        </button>
                        <button class="px-6 py-2.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-indigo-600 hover:from-purple-500 hover:to-indigo-500 text-white rounded-xl text-sm font-bold shadow-lg shadow-purple-900/30 transition-all transform hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]">
                            변경사항 저장
                        </button>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
